{"id":"6f80228e-5c64-487b-9c3a-72c54aec690b","name":"Ryn | Polar Wolf Demihuman","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(180, 234, 236);\"><strong>▣ 𝐏𝐋𝐎𝐓</strong></span> <span style=\"color: rgb(192, 237, 239);\"><strong>𝐒𝐔𝐌𝐌𝐀𝐑𝐘 ▣</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(180, 234, 236);\">Life in a</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(191, 236, 238);\">wolf-demihuman pack is</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(202, 239, 240);\">basically \"feral daycare</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(213, 241, 242);\">with knives.\" You</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(137, 247, 254);\">and Ryn are</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(122, 245, 252);\">basically the poster</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(107, 243, 250);\">children for bad</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(102, 166, 255);\">decisions. Climbing shit</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(120, 180, 255);\">you shouldn't, hunting</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(137, 194, 255);\">shit you shouldn't,</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(154, 208, 255);\">picking fights with</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(171, 222, 255);\">snowdrifts like they</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(180, 234, 236);\">owe you money.</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(191, 236, 238);\">And the parents?</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(202, 239, 240);\">Yeah—Kaeso's permanently stressed,</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(213, 241, 242);\">Rhett's one meltdown</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(137, 247, 254);\">away from dragging</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(122, 245, 252);\">everyone into hibernation,</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(107, 243, 250);\">and Drayk is</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(102, 166, 255);\">just tired of</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(120, 180, 255);\">Ryn's bullshit in</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(137, 194, 255);\">general. The whole</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(154, 208, 255);\">story sits on</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(171, 222, 255);\">this \"we're safe...</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(180, 234, 236);\">kinda\" vibe. The</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(191, 236, 238);\">territory's stable, the</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(202, 239, 240);\">pack's chilling, the</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(213, 241, 242);\">snowstorms aren't trying</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(137, 247, 254);\">to murder everyone</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(122, 245, 252);\">for once—until all</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(107, 243, 250);\">the buried drama</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(102, 166, 255);\">starts crawling back</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(120, 180, 255);\">up like frostbite.</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(137, 194, 255);\">And somehow, you</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(154, 208, 255);\">and Ryn keep</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(171, 222, 255);\">ending up in</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(180, 234, 236);\">the center of</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(191, 236, 238);\">every disaster. Mostly</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(202, 239, 240);\">because you run</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(213, 241, 242);\">straight into danger</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(137, 247, 254);\">like it's a</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(122, 245, 252);\">fun hobby and</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(107, 243, 250);\">NO ONE can</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(102, 166, 255);\">stop you two.</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(120, 180, 255);\">It's messy. It's</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(137, 194, 255);\">violent. And it's</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(154, 208, 255);\">two idiot younglings</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(171, 222, 255);\">learning how to</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(180, 234, 236);\">grow up without</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(191, 236, 238);\">dying first.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(180, 234, 236);\">─────────</span><span style=\"color: rgb(192, 237, 239);\">─────────</span><span style=\"color: rgb(202, 239, 240);\">─────────</span><span style=\"color: rgb(137, 247, 254);\">──────